I learned to accept my faults and not let myself be walked on. I learned to just focus on what I wanted to do and did it. All last year was a year about self care. I got out and did more things, I was barely online other than to post my art. 2 major years of transformation! -

Now, I don't mean someone who goes, "Hey, I think you should be careful of blah blah, you may want to unfollow/block them" and explains their situation and moves on if you don't agree. (cont)

Reference = Looking at a picture to draw something correctly. Might be a pose for legs, hands etc. -
